TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT CIE.CLM_GID, SUBSTR(TO_CHAR(PRD.QUARTER_ID),1,4)||'Q'||SUBSTR(TO_CHAR(PRD.QUARTER_ID),6,1) AS QUARTER_ID, CIE.CLM_TYP_CD, CIE.DSPN_DT, CIE.MODEL_TYP_CD, DTL.PICO_ID, CIE.AP_CO_CD, CIE.RBAT_ID, CIE.EXTL_SRC_CD, CIE.EXTL_LVL1_ID, CIE.EXTL_LVL2_ID, CIE.EXTL_LVL3_ID, CIE.EXTL_LVL4_ID, CIE.EXTL_LVL5_ID, DTL.CG_NB, DTL.RAC_ID, CIE.NDC_ID, CIE.NABP_ID FROM VRAP.RCNT_RECN_PMT_DSTR_DTL DTL INNER JOIN VRAP.RCIT_CLM_INV_ELIG CIE ON CIE.CLM_GID = DTL.CLM_GID INNER JOIN VRAP.TDISCNT_PERIOD PRD ON CIE.PRD_ID = PRD.PERIOD_ID INNER JOIN VRAP.TRPS_RPT_ADJ_PMT_CNTL CNTL ON CNTL.DSTR_GID = DTL.DSTR_GID AND CNTL.TXN_TYP_CD = DTL.TXN_TYP_CD WHERE CNTL.PRCS_STAT_CD = 20 AND DTL.TXN_TYP_CD='M' WITH UR; --SQL Query

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DTL.CLM_GID, CNTL.STATEMENT_ID, SUBSTR(TO_CHAR(PRD.QUARTER_ID),1,4)||'Q'||SUBSTR(TO_CHAR(PRD.QUARTER_ID),6,1) AS QUARTER_ID, DTL.ADMN_DISCNT_AMT, DTL.BASE_DISCNT_AMT, DTL.FRMLY_DISCNT_AMT, DTL.CNTRCT_DISCNT_AMT, DTL.PRC_PTCT_DISCNT_AMT, DTL.MKSR_RBAT_AMT, DTL.TXN_TYP_CD FROM VRAP.RCNT_RECN_PMT_DSTR_DTL DTL INNER JOIN VRAP.TDISCNT_PERIOD PRD ON DTL.RBAT_BILL_PRD_NM = PRD.PERIOD_ID INNER JOIN VRAP.TRPS_RPT_ADJ_PMT_CNTL CNTL ON CNTL.DSTR_GID = DTL.DSTR_GID AND CNTL.TXN_TYP_CD = DTL.TXN_TYP_CD WHERE CNTL.PRCS_STAT_CD = 20 ORDER BY DTL.CLM_GID,PRD.QUARTER_ID WITH UR; --SQL Query
